<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Contrat de {{ transaction.type|capitalize }}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #1e293b; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .agency-name { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b; margin: 0; }
        .agency-details { font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
        .contract-title { text-align: center; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px; background-color: #f1f5f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 25px; }
        .section-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #0f172a; border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .grid { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .col-left { width: 30%; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; color: #475569; }
        .col-right { width: 68%; display: inline-block; }
        .terms { font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; color: #475569; background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .signatures { width: 100%; margin-top: 50px; }
        .signature-box { width: 31%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .signature-spacing { margin-left: 2%; }
        .sign-title { font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 12px; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .sign-img { max-width: 100%; height: 60px; margin: 10px 0; object-fit: contain; }
        .sign-date { font-size: 10px; color: #64748b; }
        .footer { margin-top: 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1; padding-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="agency-name">{{ settings.agency_name|default('ImmoPro') }}</h1>
        <div class="agency-details">
            {{ settings.agency_address|default('Conakry, Guinée') }}<br>
            Tél: {{ settings.agency_phone|default('+224 000 000 000') }} | Email: {{ settings.agency_email|default('contact@immopro.gn') }}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="contract-title">
        CONTRAT DE {{ transaction.type|upper }}
        <div style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px;">Réf: #TR-{{ transaction.id|format("%04d") }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Les Parties</div>
        
        <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
            <div style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">Le Propriétaire (Bailleur / Vendeur) :</div>
            <div class="grid">
                <span class="col-left">Nom complet :</span>
                <span class="col-right">{{ transaction.bien.owner.name }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <div style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">Le Client (Preneur / Acquéreur) :</div>
            <div class="grid">
                <span class="col-left">Nom complet :</span>
                <span class="col-right">{{ transaction.client.name }}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Objet du Contrat</div>
        <div class="grid">
            <span class="col-left">Désignation :</span>
            <span class="col-right">{{ transaction.bien.titre }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <span class="col-left">Localisation :</span>
            <span class="col-right">{{ transaction.bien.adresse }}, {{ transaction.bien.ville }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Conditions Financières</div>
        <div class="grid">
            <span class="col-left">Montant principal :</span>
            <span class="col-right" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">{{ transaction.montant|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }} GNF</span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid">
            <span class="col-left">Date d'effet :</span>
            <span class="col-right">{{ transaction.dateTransaction|date('d/m/Y') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Dispositions Générales</div>
        <div class="terms">
            <p><strong>Article 1 :</strong> Les parties déclarent que les informations fournies ci-dessus sont exactes et acceptent d'être liées par les termes du présent contrat généré via la plateforme {{ settings.agency_name|default('ImmoPro') }}.</p>
            <p><strong>Article 2 :</strong> La signature numérique apposée ci-dessous par les parties vaut consentement explicite et a la même valeur juridique qu'une signature manuscrite.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="signatures">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="sign-title">Le Propriétaire</div>
            {% if transaction.ownerSigned and transaction.ownerSignatureImage %}
                <img src="{{ transaction.ownerSignatureImage }}" class="sign-img">
                <div class="sign-date">Signé le {{ transaction.ownerSignedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
            {% else %}
                <div style="height: 60px; margin: 10px 0; color: #94a3b8; font-style: italic;">(En attente)</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="signature-box signature-spacing">
            <div class="sign-title">Le Client</div>
            {% if transaction.clientSigned and transaction.clientSignatureImage %}
                <img src="{{ transaction.clientSignatureImage }}" class="sign-img">
                <div class="sign-date">Signé le {{ transaction.clientSignedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
            {% else %}
                <div style="height: 60px; margin: 10px 0; color: #94a3b8; font-style: italic;">(En attente)</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="signature-box signature-spacing">
            <div class="sign-title">L'Agence</div>
            {% if transaction.agencySigned and transaction.agencySignatureImage %}
                <img src="{{ transaction.agencySignatureImage }}" class="sign-img">
                <div class="sign-date">Signé le {{ transaction.agencySignedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
            {% else %}
                <div style="height: 60px; margin: 10px 0; color: #94a3b8; font-style: italic;">(En attente)</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Document généré automatiquement le {{ "now"|date('d/m/Y') }}.
    </div>

</body>
</html>
